fees.description: Min connection fee incl GST. Fees can vary for meter type, location or other factors. All fees here www.globirdenergy.com.au/fees
For move-out customer needs a final read only. Fees can vary for meter type, location or other factors. All fees here www.globirdenergy.com.au/fees
Membership fee of $0.5896 per day equivalent to $18 per month to access wholesale price.

electricityContract.terms: Daily Supply Charge is in addition to Membership Fee.  Usage rates include fixed charges and variable ones linked to 5-min wholesale prices  (Network Losses apply). Fixed charge rates incl GST: Peak 18.26c/kWh. For additional information visit www.globirdenergy.com.au/energy-saver/wholesave
electricityContract.variation: This is wholesale-linked plan, prices change every 5 minutes. Quoted annual cost is an estimate only. Usage rate uses last financial year's wholesale spot price, a representative usage of 3900 kWh,  plus any fixed usage rate.

eligibility.description: Restricted plan. Residential customers only. Must be a Sophisticated Investor or non-pensioner. No concession card or Centrelink. Income over $100k. Not on payment plan or payment assistance. Digital comms, direct debit, no life support equipment. See full T&Cs.

solarFeedInTariff.description: If you get Feed-In, you will get a feed-in tariff linked to the wholesale price subject to a 10% allowance

electricityContract.additionalFeeInformation: Additional fees and charges may apply, please see: https://www.globirdenergy.com.au/legal/fees/
